{"word":"G3539 - νοιέω - noiéō - noy-eh'-o - Consider","slug":"G3539","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νοιέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>noiéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>noy-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Consider"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>νοιέω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Noeo</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>no-eh'-o</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to perceive with the mind, to understand, to have understanding </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to think upon, heed, ponder, consider </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G3563\">G3563</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 19:48,6 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G3563\">G3563</a>; to <i>exercise</i> the <i>mind</i> (<i>observe</i>) that is (figuratively) to <i>comprehend</i> <b><i>heed</i></b>: - consider perceive think understand. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1270\">G1270</a>, <a href=\"#/G1271\">G1271</a>, <a href=\"#/G1425\">G1425</a>, <a href=\"#/G1771\">G1771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2132\">G2132</a>, <a href=\"#/G2133\">G2133</a>, <a href=\"#/G2657\">G2657</a>, <a href=\"#/G279\">G279</a>, <a href=\"#/G3340\">G3340</a>, <a href=\"#/G3540\">G3540</a>, <a href=\"#/G3559\">G3559</a>, <a href=\"#/G3563\">G3563</a>, <a href=\"#/G4306\">G4306</a>, <a href=\"#/G4307\">G4307</a>, <a href=\"#/G453\">G453</a>, <a href=\"#/G454\">G454</a>, <a href=\"#/G5282\">G5282</a>, <a href=\"#/G5283\">G5283</a>"}]}